# 4K module guide videos — served from Supabase Storage (bbf-media-vault), never
# from source control. Paths are relative to this file (frontend/), so the rule is
# public/assets/media/guides/*.mp4 — NOT frontend/public/... which would resolve to
# frontend/frontend/... and match nothing.
public/assets/media/guides/*.mp4
